attributes.description: This dashboard provides an overview of Threat Feed IOCs collected via Google Threat Intelligence IOC Stream.

params.markdown:
[Threat Intelligence](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-9e8de699-a623-4a1b-9f63-7d641116f531) | [Adversary Intelligence](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-0b0fb6b4-d250-4e31-a56a-bb872e4c7c4a) | [Threat Feed Overview](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-95187e5c-b4a2-45ad-b6a4-d6ce68e1f43e) |[IOC Stream Threat Intelligence](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-55f5f53b-343e-4095-b61f-1089a5273d84) | **IOC Stream Overview**

This dashboard provides an overview of IOCs collected via Google Threat Intelligence IOC Stream, focusing on IOC distribution and threat analysis.

It tracks total IOCs. along with Unique files, URLs, domains, and IPs. IOCs are analyzed with breakdowns by indicator type, severity, verdict, and score. Filters refine analysis by indicator type, severity, verdict, and threat score. IOCs are analyzed by file types, countries, and tags to identify patterns.

Network insights highlight top autonomous system owners, and IPv4 ranges.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/ti_google_threat_intelligence/overview)
